{"tid":1199394,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"開多次，如果去野餐 4G LTE load 空氣請轉用 3G (H+)","createTime":"2019-06-10T13:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T10:28:35.000Z","uid":11598,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21587b8d90ce33f2bccd887cb1e269bb78b2bd4f","tid":1199394,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:03:15.000Z","msg":"由於好多人 default 都係用 4G preferred, 但係preferred嘅定義係收到 signal 而唔係收唔收到 data packet<br />\n所以啲電話好蠢唔會識自己轉落 3G <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而 3G bandwidth 好順暢 好似就嘥咗咁<br />\n因為個bandwidth 就係得咁多，當一大堆人同時喺同一個基站範圍用data嘅時候<br />\n你/其他人 好大機會就會load 空氣<br />\n呢個時候你就要手動轉落 3G, 既可以騰空 4G bandwidth俾其他唔識/唔知嘅人上得到<br />\n同時你都可以上得返 其實一般用途例如tg/whatsapp 就算碌ig都好<br />\n用3G 都唔係慢得去邊<br />\n以我琴晚喺遊行現場嚟講 大半程4G都係load空氣咁滯<br />\n去到政總直情load唔出嘢<br />\n轉3G 就好順暢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家可以留意吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faae1c835ae24c2f824f644af807c92359c8e2b3","tid":1199394,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"Android :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/YEkks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FYEkks.png&h=1aab72cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSetting &gt; Network &amp; Internet &gt; Mobile network &gt; Advanced &gt; Preferred network type &gt; 3G (preferred)<br />\n<br />\n去返 4G 都係同一個位<br />\n<br />\niOS 唔知有無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b335aa4f6ed877b105a2a1690ce8a5707dd56d90","tid":1199394,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:06:09.000Z","msg":"琴日轉左3g都load唔到<br />\n係咪干擾器太勁"},{"pid":"59438551de792773823ce4252616f0a5e663c1bc","tid":1199394,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b335aa4f6ed877b105a2a1690ce8a5707dd56d90","tid":1199394,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:06:09.000Z","msg":"琴日轉左3g都load唔到<br />\n係咪干擾器太勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能唔同台唔同掛 我SMT 4G keep住load空氣<br />\n轉3g 順到無輪"},{"pid":"fa65dcbd6e0b16fe82ecf6cbff9398d802be240a","tid":1199394,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e70fea5011445beb5e33a781fcc9a85347e45a9","tid":1199394,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf2d77b51c03c23c7f98486f5a0c145268383f0","tid":1199394,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWEgXSL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWEgXSL.png&h=29fc5d6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e227498c429923acc69385b24dd6c79bd80ef1a2","tid":1199394,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecf2d77b51c03c23c7f98486f5a0c145268383f0","tid":1199394,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWEgXSL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWEgXSL.png&h=29fc5d6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8dad5bd7c62033adf71e3ea5173ace42ae3c2e5","tid":1199394,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.